data.text: @amilizblog Really well thank you, how are you!? Xx
@Missy_B83 Exactly! Give the poor woman a break. Imagine that pressure of having to come out to face all of those people when all you want to do is go home and bond with your baby. x x

@amilizblog This!! People are far too quick to judge & she can’t win. You can just imagine the reaction she’d get if she came out in her dressing gown & slippers without having make up on or brushing her hair .. “Oh my god! Why didn’t she make an effort” etc etc. It’s a sad world we live in.
@MercedesPrunty Exactly! You have to give her credit and at the end of the day, it is her job. If she had come out looking a mess, she'd be being slated too! Poor woman can't win x
@alicespake They really do! Sillyness. Hope you are doing well :) x
@amilizblog Me too, I'd break the camera other wise lol. Plus she is royalty and they have a certain image to uphold, it probably is not something she would really want to do.
@amilizblog Exactly 🙌🏻 People just like to moan.
